flowchart LR
    subgraph Client[客户端]
        User[用户] --> UI[Web 工作台]
    end

    subgraph Server[后端服务]
        API[Web API] --> Queue[(任务队列)]
        Queue ==> Worker[插件运行时]
        Worker -.-> Audit[审计日志]
    end

    UI -->|提交转换| API
    Worker -->|产物| Artifact[(临时产物)]
    Artifact --> UI

    style UI fill:#eef6ff,stroke:#2563eb,color:#111827
    style Worker fill:#ecfdf3,stroke:#16a34a,color:#052e16
    style Audit fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#ea580c,color:#431407

